4:
Hello! Got your shipment of
ingredients right here—
10:
Welcome to the Maids' Parlor. My
name's Rain, and I'll be servin—
19:
Y-you're welcome to go home,
Milord!
22:
Rain's been a huge help! We were
short-staffed for Halloween, but now
we're doing just fine!
24:
Still not sure how I feel about it, but
Rain sure does turn a lot of heads.
28: Here's your latte, filled with love.
36:
You're pretty amazing at this. Maybe
this is your calling?
41: I'm just doing my best to help out!
45: Are you not fond of that outfit, Rain?
55:
It's just... I don't want to get too used
to wearing this!
59: Honesty is the best policy, you know.
68:
Hey, you! You've been chatting up
my Rainy-Rain a little too much!
70:
We get along much better than you!
Why don't you scram?
77:
All right, everyone! It's time to play a
special Halloween quick-draw
game we like to call... Hot and Cold:
the Duel-ality of Love!
79:
The winner will receive a photo
taken together with a maid of their
choosing! Please, line up now!
81:
Hah, perfect. I'll show you just how
compatible me and Rain are!
85:
Maid rookie Rain is the winner!
Next challenger, please!
91:
...I've been waiting a long time for
this.
93:
I can't just be your backup all the
time. I've gotta get stronger than
you!
97: All right. Let's do this then, Rain!
102:
Yeah!
On your mark, get set...
110:
Phew! Things got pretty intense
there. You're good at duels, huh?
113:
Heh... You ain't seen nothing yet. You
better be ready next time.
118:
After all that... I lost instantly...
Never got my photo...
121:
U-um... Don't worry! I understand
how you feel.
125:
You come here every day, don't
you? Your passion for maids is truly
special—
135:
You're so kind. So WONDERFUL!
You're the most beautiful angel in all
the world to me!
137:
Rain! I can't think of being with
anyone else. Please, be my partner
for life!
141: No, no, no! There's no way I—
145: Oh, that's right! I'm a guy! So there!
153:
You'll have everything you'll ever
need as long as we're together! I'm
already imagining how amazing
you'll look in a wedding dress...
161:
I-I can't, I'm sorry! I already have two
special someones right here!
164: That... That's not true... is it?!
168: It's NOT! He's making this all up—
172: We're all very special to each other.
181:
Sorry to break the news to you!
Now... we've gotta GO!
184:
Beautiful until the very end... I'll never
forget you, my angel...
190:
That was way too much for me... But
now, I can finally resume my normal
duties. I'll keep myself alert, head
held high—
194:
Hey! We heard you're going out with
Alk! Is that true?!
201:
Someone from the Crimson Blades
told us. You went on a cruise with a
sweetheart? Made a public
confession of love?
203:
Oh, Rain! There you are! We've got
another special mission for you.
You'll need to dress up again!
210: Just give me a break, already!
